{"tid":1429032,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 延遲正負皮顯示會唔會重大獲","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:43:23.000Z","uid":132802,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c795dd267e75e902117f4925a2e9cc0803157994","tid":1429032,"uid":132802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"你諗下，呢邊都已經變咗做child登，仲要由開壇就有人懷疑呢邊操縱正負皮<br />\n宜家仲要隱藏埋正負評，唔係更加雪上加霜? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留言都有正負皮開始 連登變 Facebook 都算啦，始終正負皮有個指標作用 如果評分太過一面倒會令人停一停望多兩眼個留言係咪 五毛、分化 、假膠 定係 真心巴打，對連登較的年輕受眾一定有用。<br />\n呢頭雖然因為反送中 喺傳媒曝光率高咗好多，正負評容易帶風向，但咁樣更新會唔會弄巧反拙?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfb552a59bd1471a074f5cbdee73afd673f906e","tid":1429032,"uid":35205,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"兩個鐘真係太長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1220c815a9df524ede1a09f5f2b8d33c7bfbe50","tid":1429032,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3cfb552a59bd1471a074f5cbdee73afd673f906e","tid":1429032,"uid":35205,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"兩個鐘真係太長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"太短，應該要維持半日"},{"pid":"c8f908509541f96866cc182f77895aea7a51d2d2","tid":1429032,"uid":25163,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"要靠正負皮黎判斷一件事就仆街啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣不知幾好"},{"pid":"f4ea6248f2695d257848a1cde9f196a8c054390f","tid":1429032,"uid":132802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f908509541f96866cc182f77895aea7a51d2d2","tid":1429032,"uid":25163,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":